     Created: 2026-03-19
     Description:
         Color token definitions for the Dracula theme. Deep purple background
         (#282A36) with neon pink (#FF79C6), purple (#BD93F9), and green (#50FA7B)
         accents. Inspired by the iconic Dracula color scheme.

     Architecture Notes:
         ResourceDictionary. Consumed as the first merged dictionary in DraculaTheme.xaml.
         Defines all Dock* and Panel_* keys required by Dark/ shared templates
         and PanelCommon.xaml.
     ========================================================== -->

